Step 1:Start Grade
Step 2:Input first subject marks as A
Step 3: Input second subject marks as B
Step 4: Input third subject marks as C
Step 5: Input fourth subject marks as D
Step 6:p=(a+b+c+d)/400*100
Step 7:if(p&gt;=70):
print(&#39;A+ Grade&#39;)
if(p&gt;=60 and p&lt;70):
print(&#39;A Grade&#39;)
if(p&gt;=50 and p&lt;60):
print(&#39;B Grade&#39;)
if(p&gt;=40 and p&lt;50):
print(&#39;C Grade&#39;)
if(p&lt;40):
print(&#39;D Grade&#39;)
Step 8:End Grade
